title: Rams-Seahawks, Patriots, and the Cowboys
itunes:title: Rams-Seahawks, Patriots, and the Cowboys
description:
Colin talks about the Rams-Seahawks game tonight, why he feels QB Russell Wilson is underrated, why several players want to play for the Patriots, what's concerning about the Dallas Cowboys loses, and his top three college football picks. Guests include Geoff Schwartz, Greg Cosell, Urban Meyer, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
